fulltitle: Interview with Randy Weston, Part 2 of 2
title: Interview with Randy Weston, Part 2 of 2
description: Randy Weston sat down with us to discuss his music and history. In this video, he talks about early jazz figures James Reese Europe and Noble Sissle, he recalls his early musical memories, and talks about the influences of both Duke Ellington and of Melba Liston.
